cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.IR 

The paper deals with person re-identification using deep learning techniques and image processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves metric learning and feature representation, which are related to machine learning and artificial intelligence, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The use of multiple body parts and pose information suggests that the paper may also belong to cs.MM (Multimedia), while the focus on image-based person re-identification makes cs.IR (Information Retrieval) a possible category.
